description:
Recently sold: $99,000. Newly updated 3 bedroom and 1 bathroom home available in Bird Island. Very clean, no pets and no smoking. Located in a great neighborhood with a semi-private, large backyard. Extra parking and storage shed located to the west of the house. Backyard also has a new exposed aggregate patio, landscaping, small garden and wood swing set. 

Central air (motor replaced last summer). New roof in 2011. The kitchen is open to the dining room, and has a breakfast bar. Hook ups for gas and electric stove in place. New countertops in kitchen, as well as new flooring in kitchen and all three bedrooms. Bathroom was remodeled in 2011, includes a granite countertop and new toilet. Basement is an unfinished, wide open room, with the laundry/storage room separated. Great for storage or playroom. A contractor told us 2 bedrooms, bathroom, and a family room could easily be added in the basement to expand living space. Very clean and dry basement.
